'''Hova Mensk and the Blurtones''' were a [[Band/Legends|band]] from the [[Inner Rim/Legends|Inner Rim]] Territories, founded around the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the formation of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Many critics claimed that they frequently copied another band called [[The Sozzenels]].

